OL,6,FMore than 50 pubs a month on average
OL,7,Fwere lost in England and Wales during
OL,8,Fthe first half of 2024, according to
OL,9,Fnew analysis of Government data.
OL,11,FReal estate intelligence firm Altus
OL,12,FGroup said the overall number of pubs,
OL,13,Fincluding those which were vacant or
OL,14,Fbeing offered to let, fell to 39,096
OL,15,Fat the end of June.
OL,17,FThe figure is down 305 versus the end
OL,18,Fof 2023, with the pubs either having
OL,19,Fclosed down, been demolished or turned
OL,20,Finto something else.
