OL,6,FSome pubs have been converted into
OL,7,Fother types of use such as homes,
OL,8,Foffices or even day nurseries.
OL,10,FThe north west of England lost 46
OL,11,Fpubs, the most of any region, during
OL,12,Fthe first half of 2024.
OL,14,FMeanwhile, a total of 472 pubs called
OL,15,Flast orders for the final time during
OL,16,Fthe whole of the financial year from
OL,17,FApril 1 2023 to March 31 2024.
OL,19,FPubs and restaurants took a hit during
OL,20,F2020 and 2021, closing for months at a
OL,21,Ftime during Covid-19 lockdowns.
