OL,6,FAlex Probyn, president of property tax
OL,7,Fat Altus Group, warned of a "double
OL,8,Fwhammy" of property tax rises for pubs
OL,9,Fnext April, calling on Chancellor
OL,10,FRachel Reeves to use her autumn Budget
OL,11,Fon October 30 to extend the business
OL,12,Frates relief.
OL,14,FHe added that "the last thing pubs
OL,15,Fneed is an average business rates hike
OL,16,Fof #12,160 next year through
OL,17,Finflationary rises and the loss of the
OL,18,Fdiscount".
