OL,6,FA spokesperson for the British Beer
OL,7,Fand Pub Association said: "While we
OL,8,Fknow that brewers and pubs pour
OL,9,Fbillions into the economy, their
OL,10,Fmassive contribution to society is
OL,11,Fpriceless which is why any closure is
OL,12,Fdevastating.
OL,14,F"Government must use this Budget to
OL,15,Fcut beer duty, reform business rates,
OL,16,Fand maintain 75% business rates relief
OL,17,Fso that pubs can remain a home from
OL,18,Fhome."
