OL,6,FPubs currently make an average of 12p
OL,7,Fprofit on every pint of beer once
OL,8,Ftaxes and costs have been deducted.
OL,10,FSome in the industry have also voiced
OL,11,Fconcerns over potential plans to ban
OL,12,Foutdoor smoking, including in beer
OL,13,Fgardens and outside stadiums.
OL,15,FIn August, Sir Keir Starmer said the
OL,16,FGovernment would "take decisions" on a
OL,17,Fpotential outdoor smoking ban in an
OL,18,Feffort to curb preventable deaths and
OL,19,Falleviate pressures on the NHS.
